    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-09-23T15:51:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1949-09-23T15:51:00-05:00" n="110"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d110">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">501.BB/9–2349: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Extract]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">New York</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-09-23T16:51:00-04:00"
                            >September 23, 1949—4:51 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <gloss target="#t_DelGA1">Delga</gloss> 15. Following decisions taken at <gloss
                        target="#t_GaDel1">GADel</gloss> meeting September 23:</p>
                <p>. . . . . . .</p>
                <p>2. China. Effort will be made to elicit reaction of other delegates, especially
                    of Asiatic delegates, to Tsiang’s speech.</p>
                <p>. . . . . . .</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
